      <title>纽约联储称美国面临中国工厂繁荣带来的通胀风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/china-manufacturing-drive-risks-higher-us-inflation-ny-fed-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约联邦储备银行的最新研究表明，中国在房地产低迷时期提振制造业和提振经济的努力可能会给美国通胀带来“巨大的上行压力”，并推迟货币宽松政策的启动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/china-manufacturing-drive-risks-higher-us-inflation-ny-fed-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 08:19:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
